    Mendel Sensors builds easy to use environmental sensors with best in class apps and analytics to take the guesswork out of growing, help increase yields and educate growers.
    
     As a company we strive to make smarts tools (both software and hardware) for indoor farmers growing anything from cannabis to microgreens to orchids and seedlings.
